*Uzeo* je knjigu i otišao u biblioteku. (He took the book and went to the library.)

Čujes li ga, *uzimao* je novce iz kase. (Do you hear him, he was taking money from the cash register.)

Ona je *uzela* svoju stvar i otišla. (She took her stuff and left.)

On je *uzmeo* da se ponaša kao da je u pravu. (He took it upon himself to act as if he was right.)

*Uzmite* to sa vama kada izlazite. (Take it with you when you leave.)